 EDITOR'S NOTE _ Twenty years ago, an anonymous donor left an injured hawk on <PERSON> Leonard </PERSON> <PERSON> Soucy </PERSON>'s doorstep. Whoever did it picked the right house. <PERSON> Soucy </PERSON> has since patched up thousands of birds, not to mention the occasional lame duck.
