<SECOND>BC-APN--TV Week, ADV 04,0864</SECOND>
<NOTE>$Adv04</NOTE>
<HEAD>AGENCIES AND RADIO OUT</HEAD>
<NOTE>For Release Sunday, Dec. 4</NOTE>
<HEAD>From AP Newsfeatures</HEAD>
