<TEXT>
 And dear viewer, whatever you do, avoid `` Sleepaway Camp II.'' This `` Friday the 13th'' ripoff stars <PERSON> Pamela </PERSON> <PERSON> Springsteen </PERSON> -LRB- `` Fast Times at Ridgemont High'' -RRB- as the killer counselor who dispatches campers faster than you can rev up your chainsaw. She slices and dices all over the place and does in one little darling by stuffing her down the outhouse comode. You can pretty much figure out who <PERSON> Angela </PERSON> is. The why is slightly more elusive, as it normally is in these movies. The fright level in this <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> A. </PERSON> <PERSON> Simpson </PERSON> film, which was written by <PERSON> Fritz </PERSON> <PERSON> Gordon </PERSON>, is not very high. You wo n't bite your fingernails but you might kick yourself for staying with this movie for longer than 10 minutes. _ By <PERSON> Dolores </PERSON> <PERSON> Barclay </PERSON>, <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Arts </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Editor </ORGANIZATION>.
