 There's no longer a need to whine about the cork that accidentally falls into the wine bottle. Cork retrievers are available, generally for less than $ 10. Some other wine accessories: _ Thermocool, with vacuum-sealed double sides available in contemporary or crystal cut, will keep the wine bottle cold for hours. _ Vacu-vin will keep open wine fresh for days, by removing most of the oxygen in the bottle. _ A champagne key helps remove champagne corks easily and quickly. A small air pump is an alternative.
