 recently diversified into semi-conductors, telecommunications, advanced materials and high performance ceramics. The firm also is part-owner of <ORGANIZATION> California </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Steel </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Industries </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION>, based in <LOCATION> Los </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Angeles </LOCATION>. <PERSON> Kawasaki </PERSON> had 1986 sales totaling about $ 6.4 billion.
